data.description: Welcome to your future home, a delightful residence in Frederick, CO, offering a perfect blend of convenience and future potential within the community. Nestled in a sought-after location, this home is strategically positioned with close proximity to shopping centers and schools, ensuring that daily necessities and educational needs are easily met. The ease of access to I-25 further enhances the convenience for commuting or exploring nearby attractions. Excitingly, a new shopping center is currently under construction just to the East, promising additional amenities and retail options in the near future. This property provides a comfortable living space with plenty of room, a desirable floor plan, an eat-in kitchen, and an outdoor space for entertaining. The benefits of having solar are something you don't want to miss out on! Call this gorgeous house your home — a place where accessibility meets future possibilities. Schedule a showing today to explore the charm and potential this residence in Frederick, CO, has to offer.
